4) Pass `room` into ball_index_ui:
- Change renderBallIndexUI(containerId, game, room) and call with renderBallIndexUI('balls-list', this, room).

Closing notes
-------------
This audit focuses on pragmatic, incremental improvements that materially increase stability and maintainability without changing the game's visible behavior. Prioritize seeded RNG, modularization, memory disposal, and controlled DOM/audio pooling first — they yield the highest ROI.